data.description: Are you looking for your first home or looking to downsize to one floor living, this 3 bedroom, 1 bath, and with some newer finishes Ranch is perfect for you.The minute you come inside and see the spacious kitchen which has the washer and dryer on the first floor and along with the dining room which is open to the living room all with vaulted ceilings.  Enjoy the spacious backyard with a deck and fenced backyard. Conveniently located in a great neighborhood of Springfield just minutes from shopping, parks, restaurants, and highways this wonderful home will not last!(APO)
